user.about:
I’m a retired Air Force veteran 🇺🇸, now living the dream of being a stay-at-home cat mom! 🐈🐾. My motto is “you don’t have to spend a million bucks to look like a million bucks!”

I have a love of thrifting and finding classy outfits to wear and sell. Don’t worry, all clothes are kept in a cat-free room, and our home is smoke-free as well.  So check out my finds, and if you ❤️ them, make them yours! 

🌺🌺Everything I sell is something I have worn or would wear, meaning it’s in great condition, is good quality, and fits a distinctive style profile. If we have similar tastes, please follow me and visit my closet regularly, I’m always adding new items! I offer bundle discounts, but if you see an individual item you reallllly want, send me an offer.🌺🌺

🎶 A few notes ~ When you see me list something in EXCELLENT CONDITION in the description, it means it looks like new. I wont list something as “New Without Tags” unless i personally removed the original tags myself.  But to me, EXCELLENT means “like new”. If there are any flaws at all, I will list them and show pictures. 

Also, after 20 years in a uniform, I HATE ironing so most of the items here in my closet don’t require ironing! That’s a huge plus! ➕

You can sort my closet by size, brand, etc by clicking on #classy_ladies 

Thanks for stopping by and have a blessed day!❤️
